# 3.  Gap Summary

| **Gap** | **Failure Mode Without It** | **Enforcement Point** | **Phase** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Token budget tracking | Cloud escalation overruns $1.00 threshold with no attribution by call | Middleware interceptor (ADR-027) | Phase 1 |
| Tool registry as data structure | Agent capability boundary enforced only in code; drift possible as tools are added | session startup query | Phase 1 |
| Session trust tier | Model tier (ADR-021) and action risk level (ADR-018) not independently gated by session context | Interceptor pre-dispatch check | Phase 1 |
| Crash-recovery session state | Automate persona nightly job loses workflow position on process crash; no resume path | session_state table + heartbeat | Phase 1 |
